lyrics:
[Verse]
Valerie, oh Valerie, the greatest mother alive
Her love and care, they make us thrive
She's always there, with arms open wide
A shining star, on this motherhood ride

[Chorus]
Tell me why Valerie, she's the one
Supportive and strong, second to none
She sacrifices all, for her family's bright sun
Valerie, the greatest mother on earth, bar none
